imdb.plot outline: DIY Network's Chris Grundy hosts an exciting new challenge-driven series, DIY Dominator. In each episode, Chris oversees head-to-head construction and home improvement competitions. From carpentry and bricklaying contests to welding, landscaping and deck-building challenges, three competitors battle it out to earn the DIY Dominator title and a $10,000 cash prize.
